      <title>麦克勒姆认为加拿大预算对财政轨道影响不大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/macklem-sees-little-impact-of-canada-budget-on-fiscal-track</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大央行行长蒂夫·麦克莱姆 (Tiff Macklem) 表示，总理贾斯汀·特鲁多 (Justin Trudeau) 最近的预算并未显着改变政府 11 月制定的财政轨道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/macklem-sees-little-impact-of-canada-budget-on-fiscal-track</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 19:33:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德计划首次将共同基金转换为 ETF，时机成熟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/blackrock-plans-first-mutual-fund-to-etf-flip-in-sign-of-times</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德公司(BlackRock Inc.)本周制定了首次共同基金向ETF转换的计划，加入了越来越多的资产管理公司行列，这些资产管理公司在两种结构之间单向涌入的现金中实现了这一跃升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/blackrock-plans-first-mutual-fund-to-etf-flip-in-sign-of-times</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 19:33:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
